{"type": "article", "id": 14852, "title": "月牙形瓷碗", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-14T07:09:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000307WR9dTS7jo4x6uGly.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套白色陶瓷餐具的特点在于外形，像半边月亮或一颗芸豆，根据深浅和大小有 6种不同的型号。它们打破了以往圆形或方形的碗的概念，却多了一份生动的气息。其实凹进去的地方刚好可以放手，使手可以直接握住碗或盘子。陶瓷的材料来自意大利 MPS （Manifattura Porcellane Saronno），可以直接放进烤箱。这套碗有多种组合方式，全套售价 70 欧，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/handware-porcelain-dining-set/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142245j5g3dqa8UBSILFmv.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71808511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142246RiPThyrVl25L98Zp.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73297872\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142246BHEnc2P1NzRls9Ap.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"705\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142247KTsIPuSgL7R9BaMU.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"530\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}